author: Minyvonne Burke
title: Six people shot at California house party that violated stay-at-home order
description: Six people were shot, including a juvenile, at a large house party in California that violated the state's stay-at-home order.
content:
Six people were shot, including a juvenile, at a large house party in California that violated the state's stay-at-home order.
